Developer Terms of Use
des:
Get unofficial to-the-minute stats & fun facts on the Dolphins by Fresh Digital Group. This skill isn’t sponsored or endorsed by the Dolphins.

Here’s some ways you can use the skill. We have given you many different ways for you to talk to Alexa:



General Updates:


Alexa, ask Dolphins Fan how are the Dolphins doing? 

Alexa, ask Dolphins Fan who do the Dolphins play next?

Alexa, ask Dolphins Fan Jarvis Landry (or any player's First name, Last name) touchdown update. 



Fun Facts about the Dolphins:


Alexa, ask Dolphins Fan to tell me some trivia about the Dolphins. 

Alexa, ask Dolphins Fan how many Super Bowls have the Dolphins won?
